HORAN v. HUGHES. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 2, 1904.) No. 141. Appeal from the District Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York. LeRoy S. Gove, for appellant. Peter S. Carter, for appellee.

Before WALLACE, LACOMBE, and TOWNSEND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree of District Court (129 Fed. 248) affirmed, with interest and costs.
